title.narrative: Package of quality ECD 3-6 years models and strategies for migration-affected, ethnic minority and rural children finalized and widely disseminated

target.value: 2020:Package of different models and strategies for various disadvantaged groups finalized and disseminated on multiple platforms

actual.value:
2019:ECE project for migrant children in Guizhou completed in 2019 as planned, and the model is being replicated in Linyi Prefecture of Shandong province. The pilot for rural ethnic minority children continues.
3,308 teachers and 43,076 children in Guizhou and Shandong benefitted from improved capacity
